        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Protecting Children from Chemical Weapons Act</strong></p> <p> This bill prohibits federal, state, and local law enforcement officers from using chemical weapons on minors in the course of policing activities. The term <em>chemical weapon</em> includes pepper spray.</p>]]>
        </text>
